  <brief_title>Safety Study to Assess the Potential for Adrenal Suppression Following Maximal Use Treatment With DSXS</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label, Safety Study to Assess the Potential for Adrenal Suppression Following Maximal Use Treatment With DSXS in Patients With Moderate to Severe Scalp Psoriasis</official_title>
