  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      An Open Label, Safety Study to Assess the Potential for Adrenal Suppression Following
      Maximal Use Treatment with DSXS .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate the potential of DSXS topical product to suppress HPA axis function in patients
      with moderate to severe scalp psoriasis. Evaluate the efficacy parameters and adverse event
      (AE) profiles of DSXS topical product administered to patients with moderate to severe scalp
      psoriasis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
